data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom on in the country sitting on .55-acre lot. Open floor plan, 9' ceilings, low Maintenace LVP flooring. Kitchen with lots of cabinets and island, pantry, and formal dining room. Large loft with closet, nice laundry room with cabinets, large master bedroom with large Walkin closet. Two car garage finished inside with heat and air. Great location close to Wilson, Rocky Mount, and only 45 minutes to Raleigh. Close to shopping and hospitals. This immaculate home is only two years old and is a must see. No City taxes, Duke Energy. Call for appointment today
